headline: Giant Tiger Partners with DoorDash and Uber Eats, Increasing Convenient On-Demand Delivery Access for Canadians
summary: Giant Tiger Stores Limited is making shopping even more convenient with the launch of on-demand delivery available through new national partnerships with DoorDash and Uber Eats. Now available at more than 200 Giant Tiger stores across Canada, customers can shop Giant Tiger's full assortment including family fashion, grocery, health and beauty products, and household essentials, all at Giant Tiger's low prices.
